title: U.S. population data for human identification markers
description: The primary data consist of allele or haplotype frequencies for N=1036 anonymized U.S. population samples. Additional files are supplements to the associated publications. Any changes to spreadsheets are listed in the "Change Log" tab within each spreadsheet. DOI numbers for associated publications are listed below, under "References".
